description:
This is a collection of the first two volumes of The Steve Ditko Reader, which assembles some of the earlier works of the famed artist's career and packages them together for easy consumption. The two sets feature many of Ditko's creepy-crawly terrors as well as highlighting his structured, almost enclosing art style that he was known for on Spider-Man and beyond. A real treat for fans of his work, and not to be missed.

These are both DCP editions scanned by UberSoldier. Thanks to them for their work, please seed and enjoy! :-)

